      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Mattresses alliance proposes to\nhold union ball, February %, for the\nbenefit of the striking miners in Grip\npc Creek, Colo. The trades council\nconsidered the matter last night and\ndecided to lend its assistance. The\ndance will be held in the armory. Its\nrecognition by the trades council makes\nit an official union ball."
